<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  We are pleased to inform you that your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>", has been marked as completed by <%= @freelancer.name %>.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;"><strong>Task Summary:</strong></p>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Description:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Budget:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Deadline:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Status:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.status.capitalize %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  You can now review the completed work and provide feedback. Once you are satisfied, please finalize the task to complete the process.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <%= link_to 'Review Completed Task', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;' %>
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Thank you for choosing GigHive. Should you have any questions or require assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Sincerely,<br>
  The GigHive Team
</p>